  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">MP has three seasons: blazing summer (March-June), monsoon (July-September) and a glorious winter (October-February). October to March is ideal for tiger safaris, heritage temples and river travel. Tiger reserves close July 1 to September 30 for monsoon — the best time is February when tigers congregate at dwindling water holes.</p>
